  <section id="Section589675">
    <title><anchor id="Anchor595514" role="Index"
    xreflabel="bills of materials:sequenced view of" /> <indexterm
        significance="normal" zone="Anchor595514">
        <primary>bills of materials</primary>

        <secondary>sequenced view of</secondary>
      </indexterm>Sequenced Bill of Materials</title>

    <para id="Para589676">To view how Bill of Materials component Items
    correspond sequentially to their associated Bill of Operations, select the
    "Sequenced Bill of Materials" option. The following screen will
    appear:</para>

    <para id="Para520361"><screenshot>
        <mediaobject>
          <imageobject>
            <imagedata fileref="images/PD_Disp_sequenceBOM.png"
                       id="Graphic563685" />
          </imageobject>

          <caption id="Caption520362">Sequenced Bill of Materials</caption>
        </mediaobject>
      </screenshot></para>

    <para id="Para520368">When displaying a sequenced Bill of Materials, you
    are presented with the following options:</para>

    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para520369">Item Number</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1932924">
          <para>Enter the Item Number of the manufactured Item you would like
          to view a sequenced Bill of Materials for.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para663357">UOM</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x193296c">
          <para>Inventory Unit of Measure.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para520373">Show Expired Components</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x19329b4">
          <para>Select to cause expired components to be listed in the "Bill
          of Materials" display.</para>

          <para id="Para644571">Expired components will display in red
          font.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para520374">Show Future Components</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x19329fc">
          <para>Select to cause future components to be listed in the "Bill of
          Materials" display.</para>

          <para id="Para644592">Future components will display in blue
          font.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para520375">Bill of Materials</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1932a44">
          <para>Display lists sequenced Bill of Materials components, using
          the specified parameters.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>

    <para id="Para520377">To the far right of the screen, the following
    buttons are available:</para>

    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para520378">CLOSE</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1932ab0">
          <para>Closes the screen, returning you to the application
          desktop.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para664022">PRINT</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1932af8">
          <para>Runs the report associated with this screen.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>
  </section>
